up-cycle & repeat


Our Team


We consist of a team of three innovative and motivated young business owners.

Our motivation

Our mission is to create a new platform, that allows people to have an emotional connection with the fashion industry and their clothing through our up-cycling methods and sustainable made to ordered haute couture streetwear.

Our goal is to also start a new subculture, we want to create a new era of people to have the knowledge and love and chance to change their mind set of the fashion industry and to. have the chance to make change.


Short term goal

through innovative technology and interesting designs (Holograph), we want to attracted fast fashion shoppers to experience something new, to then educate them on sustainable substitutes.



Our Team


We consist of a team of three innovative and motivated young business owners.

Our motivation

Our mission is to create a new platform, that allows people to have an emotional connection with the fashion industry and their clothing through our up-cycling methods and sustainable made to ordered haute couture streetwear.

Our goal is to also start a new subculture, we want to create a new era of people to have the knowledge and love and chance to change their mind set of the fashion industry and to. have the chance to make change.


Our Values

Transparency - We want to try and be transparent, as possible, (made to order, an up cycling value chain, sustainable / natural materials).


Education - We want to try and educate the general fast fashioners, about the problems and how buy for us can change their perspective on the industry


The creation and development of a new value chains, with our up-cycling and sustainable material production.


Our New Subculture - we want to create a connection with customers on a new level, we want to to experience the full impact of the industry so you have a greater understanding of you clothing and therefore have a greater connection.
